1
00:00:59,120 --> 00:00:59,760
Father

2
00:01:07,240 --> 00:01:08,440
Strange, isn't it?

3
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:10,480
Nida is my adopted daughter

4
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:11,960
I'm the one who

5
00:01:11,960 --> 00:01:13,560
sent her into the Death Jungle

6
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:15,920
I put her in charge of the savage tribe

7
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,200
I didn't expect that

8
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:18,920
you, Zhao Wudi,

9
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:20,720
would enter the Death Jungle

10
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:23,480
so I had her stick to you

11
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:24,960
and bring her out

12
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,240
Didn't see that coming, did you?

13
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:31,440
That's my backup plan

14
00:01:32,960 --> 00:01:33,960
Nida

15
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:36,800
You were acting too

16
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,600
What an ungrateful bitch

17
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,680
Zhao Wudi

18
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:42,280
You don't really think

19
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:44,280
I'd be your little lackey, do you?

20
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:45,840
I called you "Master"

21
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,400
and you actually thought you were the master

22
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,360
Don't forget

23
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,520
I'm the tribe's sacred maiden

24
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,160
After all we did for you

25
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:55,480
I don't need your concern

26
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:57,680
I just need to finish Father's task

27
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,720
Savages really are cold-blooded

28
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,280
I underestimated you, little savage

29
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:05,800
Back off!

30
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:07,520
I said, back off!

31
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:09,680
Su Tai

32
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,560
Don't hurt my sister

33
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:13,840
Name your terms

34
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,760
Simple

35
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:19,040
Zhao Wudi keeps working for me

36
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,480
and kills whoever I want dead

37
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:23,200
Then I'll let Shen Xingyu go

38
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,640
Otherwise

39
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,480
I'll shoot her dead

40
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,120
I agree

41
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,800
I don't trust your word

42
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,400
Eat this

43
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:39,160
It's the king of all Gu

44
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,480
the Golden Silkworm Gu

45
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,320
made especially for you

46
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,560
No!

47
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,200
Boss

48
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,000
For me,

49
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,400
you really spent a fortune

50
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:52,080
Don't eat it

51
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:52,760
Shut up!

52
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,120
Can't help it

53
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:57,000
That's what you get for being Zhao Wudi

54
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,640
So you get the strongest one

55
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:09,800
Wudi

56
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:10,560
Wudi

57
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:12,760
Wudi

58
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:16,920
Zhao Wudi

59
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:17,960
That's right

60
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:19,680
Kid

61
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,880
Once you take the Golden Silkworm Gu

62
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,640
we'll still be family from now on

63
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:27,800
Boss

64
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:30,720
Hand the target over to me

65
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:31,880
No rush

66
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,120
No rush, no rush

67
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,320
I just got my hands on Dongba

68
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,920
I need time to digest it

69
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,080
The target

70
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,120
I'll send it to you tomorrow

71
00:03:42,920 --> 00:03:43,560
Nida

72
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:44,400
Fall back

73
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,360
Brother Xingchen

74
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:10,960
It's okay

75
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:14,840
For all my calculations

76
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,800
I still missed one step

77
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:17,920
Brother Wudi

78
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,320
How did it go?

79
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:20,600
Did the plan work?

80
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,240
You fatass

81
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,640
You're too late

82
00:04:24,840 --> 00:04:25,640
Long Legs

83
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,920
What the hell do you mean?

84
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,440
Where's President Xingyu?

85
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,560
She was

86
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:34,640
taken by Su Tai

87
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,120
Su Tai?

88
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,160
Isn't he your boss?

89
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,360
Su Tai's the real boss behind it all

90
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:46,400
Oh my God

91
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,880
He hid it way too well

92
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,200
So what do we do now?

93
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,080
Given the situation,

94
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,600
I'll go back and work for Su Tai first

95
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:56,600
No, Wudi

96
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,720
You can't take orders from him

97
00:04:59,360 --> 00:04:59,840
Bro

98
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:01,720
With things like this,

99
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,440
I don't have a choice

100
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:03,800
How about this:

101
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,400
you go get reinforcements

102
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,200
we'll wait for the right moment

103
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,400
By yourself...

104
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:10,720
will you be okay?

105
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:14,240
I'll be fine

106
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,760
We found Dawa

107
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,720
He's heading here tonight

108
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:30,560
The safe house

109
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,360
Youyou's safe house

110
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:47,040
Wudi

111
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:48,080
What's going on over there?

112
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:50,680
He's missing

113
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:52,960
Maybe even dead

114
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,880
There's no CCTV over there,

115
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,480
but where you came in,

116
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,600
there's a black car parked

117
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:58,720
Its dashcam

118
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,880
should've caught something

119
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:01,720
Okay

120
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,640
It really was Dawa

121
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,040
Wudi

122
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,960
I've found Dawa's trail

123
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,960
I'll send you the address right now

124
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:44,680
Zhao Wudi

125
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,240
Get angry

126
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,680
Only when rage clouds your mind

127
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:52,320
will you make an unforgivable mistake

128
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:10,680
Brother Wudi

129
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:11,760
I've been trying to reach you

130
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:12,800
I've been looking everywhere for you

131
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,320
What do you want with me?

132
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:15,800
Master Hong is dead

133
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,840
Su Tai is the mastermind

134
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,040
Let's join forces

135
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,120
and take out Su Tai

136
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,720
Take out Su Tai

137
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,640
Where's Youyou?

138
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,320
I don't know

139
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:40,560
You were the only one who went to her place last night

140
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,760
I just wanted to reach you through Youyou

141
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:45,200
I really don't know where she is

142
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:50,000
Before Youyou vanished, only you went there

143
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:52,120
If it wasn't you, who else could it be?

144
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,320
Brother Wudi

145
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:56,080
I may be an asshole

146
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:58,480
but I'm not blind to what's going on

147
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,080
Su Tai

148
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,400
It had to be Su Tai

149
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:02,840
He set me up

150
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,480
I don't care if what you're saying

151
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,480
is true or not

152
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,880
I'm out of patience with you

153
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:10,400
Today

154
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,640
you have to die

155
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,520
Nice work

156
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,000
Kid

157
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,200
Sit

158
00:08:38,680 --> 00:08:39,240
Boss

159
00:08:40,160 --> 00:08:41,440
Is Youyou in your hands?

160
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,760
What's the point of grabbing Youyou now?

161
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:46,600
I have no reason to mess with a hooker

162
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:47,640
Master Hong is dead

163
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,040
Dawa is dead too

164
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,600
Dongba right now

165
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:53,400
needs someone who can really control the situation

166
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,400
That person

167
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,440
is me

168
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,520
I need your help

169
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:02,160
A smart man knows which way the wind blows

170
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:03,600
You're a smart man

171
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,160
But boss

172
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,680
the mess Master Hong left behind

173
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:10,880
isn't small

174
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,640
Dawa may be dead

175
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:14,480
but the people behind him

176
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,200
and Master Hong's remaining assets

177
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:18,120
are all watching

178
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:20,320
None of that is the real problem

179
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:22,320
The real problem right now

180
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,000
is only one person

181
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:25,720
Sister Fei

182
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:26,720
Right

183
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,840
But before we deal with her

184
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:31,080
you need to help me eliminate someone first

185
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,200
Ali

186
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,320
She only cares about money, not people

187
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,200
Why kill her?

188
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,480
Don't lie to me

189
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:46,200
She's your old flame

190
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:48,520
She didn't just save you several times

191
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,360
she even saved your wife

192
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,320
If she doesn't die

193
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,480
I won't feel safe

194
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:55,040
And I also want to see

195
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,960
between Shen Xingyu and her

196
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:00,200
who you'd choose

197
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,760
What?

198
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,440
Dawa's dead

199
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,440
and now it's my turn?

200
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:13,880
Xingyu is in their hands

201
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,000
I don't have a choice

202
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:24,920
Zhao Wudi

203
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:27,440
You can really bring yourself to kill me?

204
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:29,360
I thought

205
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,800
I had at least a little place in your heart

206
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:48,320
Ali

207
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,680
Why did you get into this line of work?

208
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:52,320
I didn't have a choice

209
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:57,960
Who doesn't long for freedom

210
00:10:58,160 --> 00:11:00,120
and an honest life out in the open?

211
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,880
But in my line of work

212
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:05,600
once you're exposed to the light

213
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,960
the people I've offended

214
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:11,400
will put a gun to my head

215
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:18,600
If I ever got another chance to choose

216
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,400
I'd take it for sure
